    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美山（Aramco）削减价格时，油滑梯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/oil-slides-as-saudi-aramco-slashes-prices-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贸易风险的增加，石油暴跌，沙特阿拉伯在两年多以上削减了其旗舰原油价格。彭博中东能源市场记者安东尼·迪·保罗（Anthony Di Paola）加入了地平线中东和非洲的乔曼娜·贝塞（Joumanna Bercetche）。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/oil-slides-as-saudi-aramco-slashes-prices-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲最昂贵的住房计划城市修复了640亿美元的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/africa-s-most-expensive-city-for-housing-plans-fixes-for-64-billion-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开普敦是非洲最昂贵的房地产城市，计划使成千上万的房屋涌向大都市，以使其更加美好的生活质量，从而对其1.2万亿兰特（640亿美元）的住宅物业市场施加压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/africa-s-most-expensive-city-for-housing-plans-fixes-for-64-billion-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在全球紧张局势上升，新西兰加大国防支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/new-zealand-ramps-up-defense-spending-amid-rising-global-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰将增加国防支出，占国内生产总值的2％以上，旨在在与中国在太平洋的中国紧张局势加剧的情况下建立现代的，具有战斗力的军事力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/new-zealand-ramps-up-defense-spending-amid-rising-global-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 04:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>解码特朗普在造船中挑战中国的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/decoding-trump-s-plan-to-challenge-china-in-shipbuilding-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统希望挑战北京的造船能力。美国提出了对中国建造的船只或由一家中国公司经营的船只，该公司在美国港口停靠。海事战略中心的约翰·麦考恩（John McCown）和水星集团的安东·波斯纳（Anton Posner）分析了这一举动对全球贸易的影响。  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/decoding-trump-s-plan-to-challenge-china-in-shipbuilding-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 04:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自6月以来，印度股票大多数人都会大多数，因为全球增长恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/indian-stocks-slump-most-since-june-as-global-growth-fears-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股票周一暴跌，加入了从东京到悉尼的基准，因为投资者对不断扩大的贸易战争的风险及其对全球经济增长的影响做出了反应]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/indian-stocks-slump-most-since-june-as-global-growth-fears-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 03:59:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
